These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, scrabble, backgammon
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, board-games, magic-tricks, cooking
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, entrepreneur, accountant, bartender
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, horse, rat
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
 3. the firefighter is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 4. the accountant is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 7. the entrepreneur is the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the rat and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
10. the person playing monopoly is the owner of the rat##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | scrabble  | monopoly    | backgammon    | billiard   |
| Hobby   | board-games     | rock-climbing   | magic-tricks       | cooking    |
| Job   | entrepreneur | firefighter | bartender    | accountant |
| Pet           | hamster | rat       | chinchilla | horse     |

