.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, domino, billiard
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, soy-milk, juice
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, indian, mexican, spanish
City: rome, venice, hamburg, boston
 1. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
 2. the indian is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 4. the person playing poker is the colombian##1
 5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 6. the colombian is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 7. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 8. the spanish is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
 9. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
11. the mexican is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Game          | mah-jongg  | poker    | domino     | billiard       |
| Beverage         | soy-milk | juice | cola   | iced-tea |
| Nationality   | mexican | colombian   | indian   | spanish    |
| City         | hamburg | boston  | rome | venice   |

