.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, trance, salsa, dubstep
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, helicopter, skateboard, van
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, scientific, zombie, adventure
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 2. the person driving the helicopter is the fan of salsa##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 4. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 5. the person drinking juice is the fan of dubstep##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the person watching epic movies is the person driving the van##1
 8. the fan of dubstep is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
10. the person watching epic movies is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | sprite    | juice      |
| Music-Genre           | salsa | reggae | trance | dubstep     |
| Transport   | helicopter      | van   | roller   | skateboard |
| Movie-Genre           | adventure         | epic       | zombie  | scientific       |

