.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different games are played: chess, bridge, monopoly, go
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, oliveros, montecristo, tiparillo
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, sudoku, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, may, april
 1. the person playing chess is the chaman-smoker##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
 5. the person playing bridge is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 7. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person playing monopoly is the tiparillo-smoker##1
12. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Game   | go       | monopoly   | chess   | bridge   |
| Cigar       | oliveros        | tiparillo | chaman    | montecristo       |
| Hobby      | woodworking | chess    | sudoku  | card-games |
| Birthday      | july  | may  | june | april    |

