.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, trike, taxi, helicopter
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, fonseca, montecristo, havana
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, black, amber, mauve
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, skiing, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the montecristo-smoker is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person driving the helicopter##2
 3. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the person who likes black is the person driving the boat##1
 5. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
 6. the alhambra-smoker is in an even position##4
 7. the person driving the trike is the person who likes ebony##1
 8. the montecristo-smoker is the person who likes black##1
 9. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
10. the person who likes black is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
12. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Transport    | taxi    | helicopter      | boat          | trike    |
| Cigar   | fonseca | havana       | montecristo | alhambra |
| Color     | mauve     | amber      | black     | ebony |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | snowboarding | skiing        | cricket   |

