The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, april, august
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, subway, trike
 1. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 5. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 9. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
11. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
12. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Flower   | orchid | iris    | zinnia  | daisy      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea      | tea | lemonade | almond-milk   |
