4 different games are played: poker, bridge, monopoly, mah-jongg
4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, horse, turtle
 1. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the horse##2
 3. the person playing poker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
 4. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
 8. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 9. the owner of the dog is between the person playing poker and the person driving the bus##2
10. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
11. the cain-smoker is in an even position##4
12. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
