The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, snowboarding, water-polo
 1. the colombian is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4
 3. the person who growspoppy is between the person playing backgammon and the person who's sport is skiing##2
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person playing go##1
 5. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the mexican##1
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the american is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
11. the american is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who growslily is on the left of the mexican##1
13. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
