The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, scientific, epic
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, van, jet-ski, subway
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, rugby, sailing
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 3. the person watching documentary movies is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
10. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4
11. the person driving the bike is the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
| Hobby      | traveling      | drawing      | reading           | baking |
| Movie-Genre           | epic | documentary | scientific | disaster        |
| Transport   | jet-ski      | subway  | bike          | van      |
