City: marseilles, prague, berlin, colone
House: modern, craftsman, townhouse, farmhouse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, house, blues, d&b
 1. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
 2. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
 3. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the modern house##3
 4. the fan of d&b is between the person traveling to marseilles and the townhouse house##2
 5. the person eating plum is the person traveling to prague##1
 6. the fan of blues is in an odd position##4
 7. the person eating mango is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 9. the person eating raspberry is in an odd position##4
10. the fan of country is the person traveling to berlin##1
11. the person traveling to colone is on the far left or far right##3
12. the modern house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
13. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |   3    |     4      |
