 4. the fan of jazz is between the davidoff-smoker and the fan of trance##2
 5. the dannemann-smoker is between the fan of country and the fan of trance##2
 6. the swisher-smoker is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
10. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Game      | billiard   | domino   | snooker     | whist   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | jazz       | trance | house |
| Cigar           | davidoff     | dannemann   | swisher     | old-henry     |
| Sport         | volleyball | ice-hockey | handball   | cycling |

