.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, poppy, balloon-flower, amaryllis
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, pear, pineapple, apricot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, sports, western
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, journalist, videographer, security-guard
 1. the journalist is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 2. the security-guard is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
 5. the writer is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 6. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 7. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
10. the videographer is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person eating kiwi is the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Flower      | balloon-flower       | poppy | dahlia        | amaryllis        |
| Food         | apricot | pineapple       | kiwi | pear |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | satire        | mystery    | sports      |
| Job         | journalist     | videographer    | security-guard | writer   |

