.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, mauve, apricot, aquamarine
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, domino, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, rugby, water-polo
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, fantasy, documentary, thriller
 1. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing chess##2
 3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 6. the person who likes mauve is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
 8. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
10. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4
11. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
12. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Color   | mauve      | azure | aquamarine     | apricot        |
| Game   | domino | chess  | backgammon     | mah-jongg |
| Sport         | parkour    | cycling | rugby      | water-polo |
| Movie-Genre     | thriller | fantasy     | documentary | mystery       |

 